      <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;color:#1E293B;margin:20px 0 8px">No Tracking. No Advertising.</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:16px">StudyBuddy does not use any advertising cookies, analytics tracking cookies, or third-party tracking scripts. We do not share any data with advertisers.</p>

      <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;color:#1E293B;margin:20px 0 8px">How to Delete Your Data</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:8px">You can remove all StudyBuddy data from your browser at any time:</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:8px">• <strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings → Privacy and Security → Clear browsing data → Cookies and site data</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:8px">• <strong>Safari:</strong> Settings → Safari → Clear History and Website Data</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:16px">• <strong>Firefox:</strong> Settings → Privacy &amp; Security → Clear Data</p>

      <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;color:#1E293B;margin:20px 0 8px">Your Consent</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:16px">By using StudyBuddy, you consent to the use of localStorage as described above. Since we only store data locally on your device and never track or advertise, no cookie consent banner is required under most privacy regulations — but we believe in being transparent about everything we do.</p>

